17 inmate during such period of retention, unless the actual daily cost
18 as determined by the Department of Corrections Daily Rate as defined
19 in this section, exceeds Twenty-seven Dollars ($27.00) Thirty-two
20 Dollars ($32.00). If the actual daily cost as determined by the
21 Department of Corrections Daily Rate county exceeds Twenty-seven
22 Dollars ($27.00) Thirty-two Dollars ($32.00), the county shall
23 notify the Department of Corrections of the actual daily cost no
24 later than September 30. If the county’s actual daily cost is
